:{{A|VO side1 tp bronya 105.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' I'm sure you heard pieces of Belobog's history the first time you visited &mdash; the Legion's invasion 700 years ago, how the Stellaron brought about the Eternal Freeze...
:{{A|VO side1 tp bronya 106.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' It seems that much of Belobog's history from that time was buried deep beneath the snow. Those memories were lost and weren't passed down to the subsequent generations of Supreme Guardians.
----
:{{tx}}
----
