:{{A|VO side1 tp bronya 121.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' ...Now I must ask you and the Astral Express for help. Do you think you could persuade Topaz to reevaluate the situation? The Express' reputation precedes it, perhaps there's still hope...
:{{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 189.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Have no fear, Bronya! When a friend's in need, the Nameless will always be at their side!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's go have a chat with Topaz.
::{{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 190 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 190 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Yeah, after all, (Trailblazer) is a pretty good negotiator.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's bring out the big guns.
::{{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 191.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Uh... I don't think we're at that stage yet. Miss Topaz seems like a reasonable person.
::{{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 192 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side1 tp mar7th 192 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' With (Trailblazer)'s silver tongue, I'm sure we'll make some progress.
:{{A|VO side1 tp bronya 122.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' Thank you so much, both of you. I'm so sorry for dragging you into more trouble.
:{{A|VO side1 tp bronya 123.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' While you're out looking for Topaz, I'll see if I can think of a strategy to deal with the situation. Best of luck, and stay safe.
----
{{Dialogue End}}

